Kenya's Nairobi Stock Exchange to Begin Share Sale by April, Nation Says

-- B y   P a u l   R i c h a r d s o n
-- 
2011-02-18T04:52:03Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-18/kenya-s-nairobi-stock-exchange-to-begin-share-sale-by-april-nation-says.html
Shares in the  Nairobi Stock Exchange 
are expected to be sold to the public by April, the  Daily Nation 
reported, citing Capital Markets Authority Chief Executive
Officer Stella Kilonzo.  The proposed separation of ownership and management of the
bourse is part of a program to deepen capital markets in the
East African nation, the Nairobi-based newspaper said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Paul Richardson at 
 pmrichardson@bloomberg.net  